### Create a New Pet (POST)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/pets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rex",
  "owner": "Alice",
  "type": "dog",
  "race": "German Shepherd",
  "realAge": 3
}

Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri http://localhost:8081/api/pets `
-ContentType "application/json" `
-Body '{"name": "Rex", "owner": "Alice", "type": "dog", "race": "German Shepherd", "realAge": 3}'

### Get All Pets (GET)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/pets

### Update a Pet (PUT) - Replace 1 with the actual ID returned from the POST
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/pets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Reximus",
  "owner": "Alice",
  "type": "dog",
  "race": "German Shepherd",
  "realAge": 4
}

### Delete a Pet (DELETE)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/pets/1